OL,3,CSinkhole swallows two cars waiting at
OL,4,Ctraffic lights in Nebraska
OL,6,FDramatic footage has captured the
OL,7,Fmoment a sinkhole engulfed two cars in
OL,8,FNebraska.
OL,10,FA traffic camera filmed the two
OL,11,Fvehicles waiting at a red light on an
OL,12,FOmaha street on Tuesday afternoon
OL,13,Fbefore they both fell into the
OL,14,Fsinkhole that opened up beneath them.
OL,16,FPassersby and other drivers rushed to
OL,17,Fthe motorists' rescue before emergency
OL,18,Fservices arrived. Rescue crews later
OL,19,Ftowed the red car and silver truck
OL,20,Faway and began removing concrete from
OL,21,Fthe sinkhole.
