OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772161198
OL,3,CSinkhole swallows two cars waiting at
OL,4,Ctraffic lights in Nebraska
OL,6,FOmaha police say no injuries were
OL,7,Freported, but the section of the
OL,8,Fstreet would be closed for several
OL,9,Fdays, warning drivers to avoid the
OL,10,Farea as it was possible the sinkhole
OL,11,Fwould expand.
OL,13,FPosting on X, the Omaha Police
OL,14,FDepartment said: "Please avoid the
OL,15,Farea of 67th & Pacific St. The road
OL,16,Fhas collapsed and a sinkhole has
OL,17,Fopened up. Pacific St. is closed from
OL,18,F66th-69th St. Vehicles are still
OL,19,Fpermitted to travel on 67th St."
